Days in Daechuri reports that[ 22,000 riot police and 450 contracted
construction workers and thugs invaded and occupied the villages of Daechuri
and Doduri today (Sept ~~14~~ 13) at dawn and demolished 68 farm
houses.](http://saveptfarmers.org/blog/2006/09/police_invade_daechuri_and_dod.html)
The operation is to clear the land for the construction of U.S military base.

Ohmynews also have [detailed citizen report (kr) with photos showing how peace
activists and artists defended the
villages](http://www.ohmynews.com/articleview/article_view.asp?at_code=359437&ar_seq=2).

